title: STUNNING DOUBLE CEILING CORNER IN ICON BRICKELL!!
posting_body: ['Stunning 3 bedroom/ 2 bathrooms corner with magnificent water views from every room, 3 walk in closets, wood floors, brand new washer and dryer, high ceilings, spacious and tasteful unit unfurnished, automatic window treatment, Subzero/Wolf kitchen appliances in one of the most luxury and well located complex in the heard of Miami.', '5 stars pool, spa, gym, theater, concierge, valet, well known restaurants and much more.', 'A walking distance to Brickell City Centre.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
